Ingredients:
- Curd
- Chilli
- Cumin Powder
- Onion

Directions:
	Cut the chill and onion into small pieces. Take a bowl containing the curd and 
	mix it with three tablespoon of water. Mix the cumin powder,chilli and onion 
	we cut earlier and stir for a while. Leave it for 10-15 minutes for marinating 
	it. Then you have your raita is ready to be served.